lockquote><br />\nAdelaide <br />\nYear 幾就唔講啦香港人讀醫科係澳洲其實唔多"},{"pid":"bf3c22180f40d9eba50eb6e2584e206faf176c34","tid":382130,"uid":125192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:09:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想讀營養學，有冇推薦？</blockquote><br />\n你講書定係乜嘢先？"},{"pid":"2da2f3968497e7e0f6016f511928fcba366998ba","tid":382130,"uid":125192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:09:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>經second degree入？</blockquote><br />\n唔係foundation +PQA"},{"pid":"fe6bea219e1fd10bf01518a7b1a6a39c37ea0229","tid":382130,"uid":55396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:11:22.000Z","msg":"聽講澳洲醫生太多 事實係咪咁？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35b4790a9fbcd8a487edf5ca9d5baa23c5ec39e","tid":382130,"uid":125192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一日溫幾多個鐘書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個sem有冇睇幾千頁書<br />\n點記哂入腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAnatomy 就辛苦D囉，我個人鍾意買flash card ,帶住係身會容易啲記<br />\n我就冇咩計自己睇咗幾多，但係可以講話係有好多好多reading。<br />\n一日至少三四個鐘啦，五點鐘放學就食埋飯，八點鐘溫到一點囉"},{"pid":"f8d585b21f8ab7652e72b380f5115a1d6daa154d","tid":382130,"uid":125192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講澳洲醫生太多 事實係咪咁？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀尤其是international ge inter quota 係有限係爭得好辛苦。<br />\n如果唔係就要去一啲rural 到做，或者去其他城市"},{"pid":"b8bc37b26a8e1a2a81ed614bd2ed78c87bb95455","tid":382130,"uid":125192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:13:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講澳洲醫生太多 事實係咪咁？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過其實好咗因為其他大學包括我自己個間都收少咗好多人，起碼收小左3-40人"},{"pid":"5c5f8eaa402d7e4c184f5065e72b96b71a7a275e","tid":382130,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:15:38.000Z","msg":"Al/dse咩成績？"},{"pid":"300cd249ef926af93d3ace7f7ba8114794bf5289","tid":382130,"uid":55396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:17:18.000Z","msg":"國際生學費幾多？ 有無獎學金/funding？同埋識唔識有香港學生黎讀2 nd degree"},{"pid":"5840c47f3eb6735ee210dace90a5507379300b2c","tid":382130,"uid":125192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:17:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Al/dse咩成績？</blockquote><br />\n直情讀foundation ,嗰陣成績92%<br />\nDSE以我所知好似收30<br />\nAlevel 坐底要2-3A*+1-2A<br />\n其實香港人要入鏡唔難囉最難嘅係佢哋嘅性格測試"},{"pid":"da0daef3384664f7cad079f87c579b72b918acc7","tid":382130,"uid":125192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:18:11.000Z","msg":"ISAT/PQA 係踢得最多人同最難嘅一部份"},{"pid":"1d3d7c07b095e765ac73b1ed512901dedb3d7363","tid":382130,"uid":125192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T02:19:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國際生學費幾多？ 有無獎學金/funding？同埋識唔識有香港學生黎讀2 nd degree</blockquote><br />\n香港學生以我識嘅全部都係Alevel/IB<br />\n依家以我所知大部份med school都收6-7萬AUS per year <br />\n奬學金佢哋通常都係留俾本地學生多啲，基本上好少會比到international ,尤其係香港學生"},{"pid":"6667fa8b7239bcc3809c6fead2b86634c6ebab82","tid":382130,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>經second degree入？</blockquote><br />\n唔係foundation +PQA</blockquote><br />\n咩叫pqa<br />\ngamesat(唔識串) d fd?"},{"pid":"8a667cd2d18be6a6969751112f599912c35e62e6","tid":382130,"uid":125192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T10:05:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>經second degree入？</blockquote><br />\n唔係foundation +PQA</blockquote><br />\n咩叫pqa<br />\ngamesat(唔識串) d fd?</blockquote><br />\n對唔住遲咗覆因為有嘢做<br />\n係呀<br />\n但係PQA只係小部份嘅大學認可"},{"pid":"01798dcaf19f79c8bb13b3a0c70559fca93554de","tid":382130,"uid":73462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:17:45.000Z","msg":"有冇信心回流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50335aa87277d789138fbda1c80e8d6f16905f30","tid":382130,"uid":125192,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:20:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇信心回流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港執業試好似好難，我都有D擔心。希望香港可以參考下新加坡咁，認可一啲世界高排名嘅大學，免除執業試。咁樣嘅話又唔需要請啲大陸醫生，又可以有快速人手補給"},{"pid":"cfd75c5c673f7ffe15ed0191a3c839222e5506ab","tid":382130,"uid":24597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:20:41.000Z","msg":"巴打溫醫有無心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無回流心得分享下"},{"pid":"08d4047b33a0a562c6f21e823a8ea608b97bd87f","tid":382130,"uid":129866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:15:24.000Z","msg":"Doesn't it make more sense to complete a UG degree somewhere decent in Australia first, and see if you have a shot at UniMelb/USyd's MD program? It's definitely going to cost a lot, and it's hard to tell how you are going to rank up against the rest of the applicants. But what's the rush for going straight into a second tier MD in Australia that has a reputation way inferior to those so called &quot;second tier&quot; MBBS programs in the UK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55fcd2a3e392a4d0ddb0f09f1a8a2f03eb84d75a","tid":382130,"uid":139322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇信心回流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港執業試好似好難，我都有D擔心。希望香港可以參考下新加坡咁，認可一啲世界高排名嘅大學，免除執業試。咁樣嘅話又唔需要請啲大陸醫生，又可以有快速人手補給</blockquote><br />\n班老屎忽點會容許人攪壞佢地個小圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}